          <li class="list-group-item text-center">📋 View all scheduled tweets from the <strong>"Tweets"</strong> page.</li>
          <li class="list-group-item text-center">✏️ Edit or delete your tweets anytime.</li>
          <li class="list-group-item text-center text-danger">⚠️ Deleting a connected Twitter account will remove all linked tweets.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
